snippet.textDisplay: How in the hell have I not heard and watched this for a full two years?!! What an EXCEPTIONAL track and what an absolute delight to watch and hear these gorgeous voices and watch their taal-mel. Fantastic song. I appreciate the subtitles considering I do not speak or know Punjabi, but these lyrics hit close to home. The truth in the lyrics takes the song to an entirely new level of amazing. Massive respect and genuine appreciation for both Maan ji and Diljit's talents.
